.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

City: miami, edinburgh, marseilles, london, hamburg
There 5 different types of food: blueberry, kiwi, zucchini, peas, pineapple
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: handball, weightlifting, cycling, basketball, swimming
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: miamimaster, poppy, iris, daisy, azalea
The people have 5 different jobs:  scientist, musician, firefighter, mechanic, paramedic
1. the person eating blueberry is the person traveling to marseilles
2. the person eating swedish is the firefighter
3. the person eating kiwi is the person who's sport is basketball
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to london
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who's sport is weightlifting
6. the person who growsiris is the musician
7. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who growspoppy
8. the person who's sport is cycling is in the middle
9. the person eating peas is on the far left
10. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the scientist
11. the paramedics is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy
12. the person who growsmiamimaster is the person who's sport is handball
13. the person eating zucchini is the person who growsdaisy
14. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami
15. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| City		|    hamburg	|     miami	|      marseilles	|     edinburgh	|     london	|
| Food	|   peas	|    kiwi	|    blueberry	|    zucchini	|    swedish	|
| Job		|     scientist	|    paramedic	|     musician	|     mechanic	|      firefighter	|
| Sport	|    swimming	|     basketball	|     cycling	|    weightlifting	|      handball	|
| Flower		|   poppy	|    azalea	|  iris	|    daisy	|   miamimaster	|
